These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, time-travel
There 2 different types of food: onion, spinach
House: cottage, gothic-revival
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, disco
1. the person eating spinach is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
2. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
3. the fan of disco is on the right of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Movie-Genre      | time-travel      | fantasy    |
| Food           | spinach | onion |
| House   | cottage       | gothic-revival  |
| Music-Genre     | gospel      | disco     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, september
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, milk
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, daffodil
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, water-polo
1. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Birthday          | september | january |
| Beverage   | sprite       | milk         |
| Flower           | daffodil     | zinnia         |
| Sport     | water-polo    | swimming    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, tea
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, october
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, zombie
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, brown
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person who likes brown is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
4. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Beverage         | tea          | mirinda |
| Birthday           | october | december     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy            | zombie         |
| Color     | brown         | red   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, blood-red
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, may
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, analyst
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the analyst##3
2. the person playing scrabble is the bartender##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Game      | scrabble     | mah-jongg   |
| Color   | blood-red    | fuchsia |
| Birthday   | december   | may |
| Job           | bartender | analyst    |

