.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-5::.
City: miami, london
2 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, lavender
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, pop
1. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the person who likes coral is on the left of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |      2       |
| City   | miami        | london        |
| Pet       | mouse       | ferret         |
| Color        | coral | lavender |
| Music-Genre      | punk   | pop       |

