3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
4. the craftsman house is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| House      | craftsman    | farmhouse   |
| City           | san-francisco | miami    |
| Cigar   | dunhill   | game  |
| Transport   | skateboard     | bus |

