.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, bongani
City: london, venice
House: farmhouse, futuristic
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, martial-arts
1. the futuristic house is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
2. the person traveling to london is the farmhouse house##1
3. the farmhouse house is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Cigar      | bongani     | chaman |
| City          | venice   | london |
| House   | futuristic     | farmhouse     |
| Movie-Genre     | drama | martial-arts     |

 